# Assistant extension — single source of truth

- **The only Assistant extension in this repo is `extension/`** (at the repository root).
- **Do not create, add, or copy the Assistant extension anywhere else.** Do not create `apps/*/source-extension/`, `apps/*/assistant-ext/`, or any second unpacked extension directory for the Assistant.
- All edits to the Chrome extension (panel, options, background, content scripts, manifest, CSS, assets) must be made in **`extension/`**.
- When running or loading the extension, use **`extension/`** (e.g. `npm start` loads it by default, or set `NEW_BROWSER_EXTENSION_PATH` to the repo path ending in `/extension` if needed).
- Reference docs and snapshots under `REF DOCS/extracted/` are not the Assistant; they are other products. The runnable Assistant is only in **`extension/`**.
